<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11124] Pluggable major compaction strategy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11124</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider adding to the master a schedulable internal task that manages major compaction. The scheduler implementation should be pluggable. The default plugin should implement the current policy, a simple interval trigger governed by a site configuration property. Reserve a znode as a store for major compaction scheduler state, allow the plugin access to (re)create it and update as needed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
